This is the protocol for a review and there is no abstract. The objectives are as follows:, We aim to conduct a systematic review of prevention and treatment strategies for constipation in children with chronic illness or in palliative care to determine which strategies, alone or in combination:, 1. relieve or prevent constipation in children with chronic illness, 2. relieve or prevent constipation in children in palliative care, 3. have short or long term outcomes, 4. cause additional harms, 5. improve the quality of life